snippet.title: ElRichMC - Minecraft & Gaming a otro nivel
snippet.description:
¿Listo para descubrir un canal creativo y sin límites? ¡Aquí podrás encontrar de todo!

Un detalle de importancia:
La mayoría de mis vídeos tienen más de 4h (90%) de trabajo detrás, pero hay muchos que superan las 8h (50%) y otros tantos que me llevan  +50h o +100h, es por eso que yo no puedo prometeros un vídeo diario, lo intento lo prometo, pero hay días o semanas en lo que todo se me complica o cualquier otra cosa que surja que hace que todo se me vaya al garete :S Pero eh! No seamos pesimistas :) Si pierdes todos tus diamantes por culpa de un doble creeper (Un creeper explota tu baúl más valioso y un segundo los items) no hay que desanimarse, piensa en lo bien que te lo vas a pasar recuperando tus tesoros!

Seguidme en mi Twitter (https://twitter.com/ElRichMC) y os tendré informado.
Sigueme en Twitch (https://www.twitch.tv/elrichmc) hago directos todos los sábados y domingos a las 17:00 hora española :)

snippet.title: Luminosity Gaming
snippet.description:
Luminosity Gaming is one of the largest globally recognized esports organizations in North America. Our headquarters is located in Toronto, Canada. Our mission is to support the communities created by our athletes, ambassadors, and creators to provide a long lasting career in professional gaming. Founded in February 2015 by Canadian-born Steve Maida. 

At the same time, we are passionately invested in the growth of esports and contribute to it's rapidly excelling growth. Enthusiast Gaming (the Parent Company of Luminosity) mission is to build the largest network of communities for gamers and esports fans. Luminosity Gaming is uniquely positioned to support the growing legion of competitors, creators, and ambassadors that have joined our #LGLOYAL community; Including powerhouse teams such as the Seattle Surge and Vancouver Titans. Stepping forward into the future has never been more exciting for us at Luminosity Gaming.

snippet.title: SaveDex Gaming
snippet.description:
Hello Friends!!! Welcome to SaveDex, a channel primarily focused on Nintendo, although we are open to other gaming companies. 

Dave and Sophie are your hosts, bringing you game reviews, live streams, top 10s and some comedy skits involving puppets (mainly Tom Panda). Dave is also on a mission to Break His Backlog this year too. Sharing the experience through the live streams, followed by a review of that game.

Enjoy your time on our channel and thanks for checking us out.

snippet.title: Hood Gaming
snippet.description:
On Hood Gaming, you will be able to find Football Manager 2023 guides, wonderkid videos, the best FM23 tactics and rebuild challenges.  

For this year's game, I will be live streaming my Versailles FC save on Monday - Thursday evening's 7pm - 9pm. 

𝘼𝙗𝙤𝙪𝙩 𝙈𝙚

I have always made content throughout my professional career, however, it has always been for someone else. In May 2020 I decided that it was time to create something for myself. Football Manager has always been a game that I have loved so wanted to take this opportunity to share some of the tips and tricks that I've learnt!
